Key Match Events: Juan Soto hit a home run in the 6th inning, scoring Gleyber Torres.
In the 11th inning, Dairon Blanco stole third base and scored on a wild pitch by Jake Cousins.
Jazz Chisholm Jr. had an RBI single in the 10th inning, scoring Jon Berti and tying the game at 3-3.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game was played at Yankee Stadium III.
